===Etymology===
Via French ''[[koumis]]'', German ''[[Kumiss]]'', from {{etyl|ru}} ''[[кумыс]]'', from {{etyl|trk}} ''[[kumyz]]'' (akin to Turkish {{term|kımız|lang=tr}}).<ref>[http://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/koumiss "koumiss."] ''Webster's Third New International Dictionary, Unabridged.'' Merriam-Webster. 2002.</ref>

